============== EVENTBUS

About using JavaRx instead of EventBus. For EventBus disadvantages see
    https://github.com/google/guava/wiki/EventBusExplained
JavaRx has many features that are not needed for SS. Looking through the
disadvantages, there is little that affects SS.
It does have the advantages of a cleaner, albeit much more complex,
UI; more complexity for
little additional benefit. A real advantage would be if SS wants to use R8 and
Proguard. If/when SS uses more features

EventBus replacement

